recital.p:
Following an application from Vifor Ltd, submitted pursuant to Article 14(1)(b) of Regulation (EC) No 1924/2006, the Authority was required to deliver an opinion on a health claim related to Equazen eye q® and improving reading ability (Question No EFSA-Q-2014- 00462

EFSA Journal 2015;13(10):4251.
                  ). The claim proposed by the applicant was worded as follows: 'Equazen eye q® (composition of EPA:DHA:GLA at a 9:3:1 ratio) improves reading ability and related cognitive functions in children'.
